        <br/><br/> 
        
        <div class="slds-progress__item_content slds-grid slds-grid_align-spread QuestionClass">Q1. Do you have any research sponsorship agreements, consultancies with, or equity holdings in, or directorships of, companies or other organisations that might have an interest in the results of the proposed research? If yes, then please provide brief details (200 words max.) </div>
